description:
Surf the web without tracking with a VPN, shield your devices with Antivirus, & guard your identity with an all-in-one app.


What's new:

* You now have a new option to pause your VPN connection until the next day;
* We're working to improve our web content blocker — as part of that, we removed the two-factor authentication (2FA) option from its settings;
* As always, we added some stability improvements and performance refinements across the app.
